x; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; border-top-width: initial; border-right-width: initial; border-left-width: initial; border-top-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 165, 45);\">为啥 Blazor 的组件都很丑？</a></p> \n</blockquote> \n<figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> \n <img src=\"https://files.mdnice.com/user/54322/9694021a-7874-4e7e-8bcd-80fb4d09a05a.png\" alt=\"讨论\" style=\"display: block; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 15px; height: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; object-fit: fill; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"> \n <figcaption style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: center; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n   讨论 \n </figcaption> \n</figure> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px;\">仿佛击中了我，何止是 Blazor 的组件丑，打我从业以来，使用微软的技术框架有没有不丑的？大部分时间都在怀疑自己的审美观，难道只有我一个人觉得丑？</p> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block; line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 2.2em; margin-bottom: 4px;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgb(81, 81, 81); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; background-image: linear-gradient(rgb(255, 255, 255) 60%, rgb(255, 177, 27) 40%); background-position-x: initial; background-position-y: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; padding-top: 2px; padding-right: 13px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-left: 13px; margin-right: 3px; height: 50%;\">流行的 Blazorise 框架</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px;\">Blazorise 是我用过的不错的 Blazor 框架了，起步比较早，在刚开始Blazor 发布的时候就有了，而且还是免费的。Blazorise 集成了很多流行的前端框架，比如 Bootstrap、Bulma、Ant Design 等等，所以你可以选择自己喜欢的前端框架。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=