t; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px;\">还记得当时带我入门的师父给我推荐了一个前端库 <code style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(155, 110, 35); background-color: rgb(255, 245, 227); padding-top: 3px; padding-right: 3px; padding-bottom: 3px; padding-left: 3px; margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 3px; margin-bottom: 3px; margin-left: 3px;\">AvalonJs</code>，我当时并没有采用，而是这个库的作者名字很特别，叫 <code style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(155, 110, 35); background-color: rgb(255, 245, 227); padding-top: 3px; padding-right: 3px; padding-bottom: 3px; padding-left: 3px; margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 3px; margin-bottom: 3px; margin-left: 3px;\">司徒正美</code>，后来陆续也看了他的一些文章，直至前几年他去世，怀念这位大神，也算是我前端的领路人。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px;\">因为从 <code style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(155, 110, 35); background-color: rgb(255, 245, 227); padding-top: 3px; padding-right: 3px; padding-bottom: 3px; padding-left: 3px; margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 3px; margin-bottom: 3px; margin-left: 3px;\">AvalonJs</code> 到 Vue，包括现在我比较喜欢用的 React、NextJs。伴随着这些前端的发展，越来越多的框架和组件库出现，而且都是很好看的。</p> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block; line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 2.2em; margin-bottom: 4px;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgb(81, 81, 81); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; background-image: linear-gradient(rgb(255, 255, 255) 60%, rgb(255, 177, 27) 40%); background-position-x: initial; background-position-y: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; padding-top: 2px; padding-right: 13px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-left: 13px; margin-right: 3px; height: 50%;\">颜值既正义</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> \n <img src=\"https://files.mdnice.com/user/54322/78970b8a-e8d9-47ce-a322-054a0703bfac.png\" alt=\"Fluent Design\" style=\"display: block; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 15px; height: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; object-fit: fill; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"> \n <figcaption style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: center; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n   Fluent Design \n </figcaption> \n</figure> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px;\">一直喜欢用微软的技术，他们的 UI 设计也一直在进步，比如现在的 Fluent Design，很喜欢，也很漂亮。相比较 material design，我更喜欢 Fluent Design，因为我觉得 Fluent Design 更加的简洁，而且更加的现代。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px;\">但是背靠微软技术的一些框架好像有什么路径依赖，好像不怎么在意界面的显示，或者说只满足于功能与逻辑。就像一些传统行业还在使用大量的 web service，WCF，asp.net 等等。相比较于 java、go、python 等生态，.net 的生态好像有点落后，这也是开源太晚、生态差、社区小的原因。</p> \n<figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> \n <img src=\"https://files.mdnice.com/user/54322/bee3b7d9-cce6-441e-9b97-4b2162d2f529.png\" alt=\"github\" style=\"display: block; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 15px; height: auto; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; object-fit: fill; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"> \n <figcaption style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: center; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n   github \n </figcaption> \n</figure> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px;\">不过也没关系，Blazor 现在是支持 ant design、tailwind css 等等的。并且可以封装自己的组件库，我在创建 Blazor 的时候，首先会排除 Blazorise、mudblazor。因为Blazor基础设施已经很完善了。稍微熟悉 tailwind css 就能做出来一个还不错的 UI 体验。</p> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block; line-height: 1.5em; margin-top: 2.2em; margin-bottom: 4px;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgb(81, 81, 81); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; background-image: linear-gradient(rgb(255, 255, 255) 60%, rgb(255, 177, 27) 40%); background-position-x: initial; background-position-y: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; padding-top: 2px; padding-right: 13px; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-left: 13px; margin-right: 3px; height: 50%;\">总结</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px;\">现在项目写的多了，是真的不想在写xaml的UI了，耗时费力，不讨好。而 Blazor 相比较而言安装包是大了一点，但是至少可以保证你的项目能和别人的 UI 项目一样好看。性能也不会差。如果你也在开发桌面软件，可以试试 Blazor。当然也可以和我交流。</p>",
